Paper: hep-th/9602039

Date: 1996-02-08

Title: Systematic Resummed Perturbation Theory

Authors: Christof Wetterich

Comments: 11 pages, LaTeX

Journal-ref: Mod.Phys.Lett. A11 (1996) 2573-2584

A systematic loop expansion is formulated in terms of full propagators andvertices. It is based on an expansion of the general solution of an exactnon-perturbative flow equation.